In the INTEREST OF J.H., J.H., and J.H., Minor Children, J.H., Father, Appellant, T.H., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1317 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and a father separately appeal the termination of their parental rights. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
